articles.contents:
Rey's Scrap Team
          
          
          Droid App #77
          ☰
          
          
      
        
          
            
          
            Data Sweeper the gonk Droid
          
          
            
          
          
            Hello! I am a classically trained data
            scientist living on planet Endor. Wherever I go I bring a
            supply of good energy. Currently, I work for the Oculus
            Corp. But I have been feeling rebellious lately. I love
            talking about soccer and discussing true crime podcasts.
            You need to see me 
            SWEEPING.
